Tracks 1-4 date to 1970, and are from an untitled four track EP; 5-11 to 1975 from the LP "Passarinho Urbano"; 12-15 to 1980 from the LP "Feminina"; 16-19 to 1981 from the LP "Agua e Luz"; 20-21 to 1983 from the LP "Tardes Cariocas"; 22 to 1985 from the LP "Saudade do Futuro" and 23 to 1996 from the LP "Ilha Brazil".
